  "prompt": "What is the average price of a wedding dress?",
  "response": "The average price of a wedding dress can vary significantly depending on factors such as brand, designer, fabric, and style. However, as of recent data around 2023:\n\n- For a standard new wedding dress from a bridal boutique, the average is typically between $1,000 to $3,000.\n- Designer dresses or dresses with high-end materials and intricate details can range from $5,000 to $10,000 or more.\n- Budget-friendly options, including off-the-rack dresses, can be found for $500 to $1,000.\n- Online retailers and second-hand dresses can be available for even less, often between $100 to $500.\n\nKeep in mind that alterations, accessories, and other related costs can add to the total expenditure for a wedding dress.",
